{
  "stem": "17299.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found out later on, they overheard a phone call that the-- that the Jews will be taken out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the Jews from Dondangen will be removed, because the Russians come near.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they two escaped to a Latvian farmer, whom they had supplied with cigarettes and tobacco, which we had stolen before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were told we are going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we had to march towards Libau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We marched only for three or four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At nights, we were out in the field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first night, quite a few Latvian Jews escaped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took, although, a number of guards along, which were German or Lithuanian guards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] on the second day, some tried to escape in daytime, and they got shot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then the Hungarian women were marching in front of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were 800 girls from Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had heard from them what Auschwitz was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time, we know what Auschwitz was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us about the gas chambers and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Dondangen-- because we gave the food to the camp and everything, we had to feed all the regiment-- had 3,800 Jewish prisoners of that day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, officially, all 3,800.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How many escaped, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We marched three days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the fourth day, we were put on a train to Libau, Liepaja in Latvian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were guards, who said, anyone who goes-- goes over the side gets shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Open boxcars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three or four hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in Libau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were put in a farm or leather factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first two days, we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the third day we got food.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
